    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>diced shallot</strong> and <strong>chopped tomato</strong> in a small bowl with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1679397118255-x200.jpg",
