            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw</strong> and <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> to a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>quick-pickled slaw</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>mayo</strong> in a separate bowl and mix it all together – this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
