            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> cornflour</strong> and <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> on a plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix it all together</p><p>Firmly press the <strong>basa fillets</strong> into the cornflour mixture, making sure to evenly coat them on both sides – this is your <strong>coated basa</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
