    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>seasoned brown rice</strong> in bowls</p><p>Top with<strong> </strong>the <strong>tomato salsa</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled slaw</strong> and <strong>crispy basa</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>chipotle mayo </strong>and garnish with the <strong>reserved coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
